<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.9">
<l>pōtārtā maraiyāḷ pulavikkula vāṉavartam</l>
<l>kōtākō tilceṅkōl kuṭaimaṉṉari ṭainaṭanta</l>
<l>tūtātū moḻiyāy cuṭarpōleṉma ṉattirunta</l>
<l>vētāniṉ ṉaṭaintēṉ tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Joy of the one of the budding lotus, of earth, [and] of the clan of celestials,</l>
<l>Messenger who walked midst faultless kings [with] scepters [and] umbrellas,</l>
<l>You of immaculate words, Veda who remains in my mind like the sun,</l>
<l>I take refuge in you, the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
